OL,8,GWhen Sam Bell signs up for a
OL,9,Gthree-year mining contract working on
OL,10,GSarang Moon base, he assumes he is
OL,11,Galone. He is wrong. Beautifully shot
OL,12,Gby Duncan Jones and with thumping
OL,13,Gmusic by Clint Mansell, Moon is dark,
OL,14,Gclaustrophobic and at times surreal.
